00:00:15.735 --> 00:00:17.655
used to using it. There's definitely a learning

00:00:17.655 --> 00:00:21.335
curve to using Emacs but it's, once you

00:00:21.335 --> 00:00:23.015
learn it, you can do lots and lots

00:00:23.015 --> 00:00:25.495
of different things. Now you may have to

00:00:25.495 --> 00:00:27.255
