00:00:36.420 --> 00:00:39.220
to show you. But we will do the

00:00:39.220 --> 00:00:41.380
best we can the best we can with

00:00:41.380 --> 00:00:45.365
this. So if we type emacs and then

00:00:45.365 --> 00:00:48.805
hello dot c will open up the file.

00:00:48.965 --> 00:00:50.965
